	transportation income under Section 883 of the Internal Revenue Code, provided less than 50 percent of its Common Units are owned by 5-percent shareholders (other than Capital
	Maritime or its affiliates) as defined in Treasury Regulation 1.883-2(d)(3) for more than half the number of days during the year of the Offering.


